---
title: Spanish Chorizo and Pepper Rice with Parsley, Almond and Lemon Sprinkle
description: Taking inspiration from the classic Paella, this Spanish Chorizo and Pepper Rice with Parsley, Almond and Lemon Sprinkle brings fresh and zesty flavours together for a taste adventure. With a little crunch from the almonds, this summery dish is a great for a family feast – ideal for al fresco dining.
